# Images skill (pointer)

Canonical: [`/skills/images/SKILL.md`](../../skills/images/SKILL.md). Read it before acting.

Key points:

- Catalog: `assets/images/photos.yaml` (version 1; `file`, `original`, `alt` sv+en+de, `tags`). **Existing rows:** use alt verbatim. **New uploads (§E):** save original to `assets/images/<file>`, new canonical `file` name, author all three alts + tags, append YAML, then copy to `site/public/…` + derivatives + wire.
- Derivatives follow `docs/responsive-image-workflow.md`: `*-SUFFIX-640w.webp`, `*-SUFFIX-960w.webp`, `*-SUFFIX-960w.jpg`. `SUFFIX` is one of `gallery`, `body`, `aside`, `hero`, `testimonial`.
- Archive masters: `assets/images/`. Served masters + derivatives: `site/public/wp-content/uploads/<year>/<month>/`. Wiring: `stockholm-body-responsive-images.ts`, `assets.ts`, `stockholm-marketing-gallery.ts`.
- Stockholm pages render both `sv` and `en` off the **same** `BodyPictureSources` constant; only the `alt=` attribute differs by locale (pull `alt.sv` vs `alt.en` from `photos.yaml`).
- **Pick and wire in one pass**; document slot, `file`, and rationale in the **PR** (user approves at merge, not a pre-merge chat pick).
- **Default components:** `ResponsiveInlinePicture`, `HeroSection`, `GallerySection` (match peer `page-bodies` unless the user specified otherwise).
- Count heuristic: location hub 4–6, experiential page 2–3, factual anchor 0–1, SEO landing 1–2.
- Verify with `npm test && npm run build` from `site/`.
- Escalate: no existing catalog match and no new file to ingest; Berlin needs an image not in catalog with no upload; single-locale Stockholm request; missing asset when wiring; colour claims vs catalog light-vs-textile rule; ImageMagick unavailable.
